Package: lisanon
Title: Anonymization Pipeline for LIS Excel Exports
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Christoph", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "your@email.com")
Description: Pre-processing pipeline for Laboratory Information System (LIS)
    exports before LLM-assisted annotation. Handles UUID mapping of case IDs,
    removal of patient identifiers, merging of free-text columns, and 
    de-identification of physician names via spaCy NER.
